title: Muir Woods National Monument: Current Conditions
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Basic Information     Current Conditions              Current Conditions        Alerts    Information        Heavy Traffic and Limited Parking at Muir Woods  Alert 1 , Severity ,information ,, Heavy Traffic and Limited Parking at Muir Woods  Parking at Muir Woods is extremely limited. Expect parking to fill very early in the day, with significant delays on Muir Woods Rd. Plan a safe, enjoyable trip by considering alternative transportation options or less busy times of the day. more
